---
// Sponsor panel
---

<div class="sponsor-panel">
  <div class="sponsor-content">
    <p>
      <span class="sponsor-intro">WebSocket.org is proudly sponsored by <a href="https://ably.com" class="sponsor-link">Ably</a></span>
      the definitive realtime API infrastructure. Ably powers more WebSocket connections than any other pub/sub platform on the planet, serving over a billion devices monthly.
      <a href="https://ably.com/" class="learn-more">
        See why devs love Ably &raquo;
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .sponsor-panel {
    background-color: #f5f7ff;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    border: 1px solid #e6e8f0;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .sponsor-content {
    max-width: 100%;
    color: #4a5568;
  }

  .sponsor-intro {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #2d3748;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .sponsor-link {
    color: #4361ee;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .sponsor-link:hover {
    color: #3a56d4;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .learn-more {
    color: #4361ee;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .learn-more:hover {
    color: #3a56d4;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sponsor-panel {
      padding: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>

